<h4 id="1-problem">1. Problem</h4>

<h4 id="2-model-architecture">2. Model Architecture</h4>

<p><img src="/images/ai-dynamic-model-kalman-filter-introduction.png" height="" width="" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Markov Property
\(\begin{aligned} p\left(x_{t} \mid x_{1}, \ldots, x_{t-1}, y_{1}, \ldots,
y_{t-1}\right) &amp;=p\left(x_{t} \mid x_{t-1}\right) \\ p\left(y_{t} \mid x_{1},
\ldots, x_{t-1}, x_{t}, y_{1}, \ldots, y_{t-1}\right) &amp;=p\left(y_{t} \mid
x_{t}\right) \end{aligned}\)</p>
  </li>
  <li>This model is copying the hidden markov model, it keeps the basic markov
properties</li>
  <li>Change itâ€™s parameters.</li>
</ul>

<p>For Kalman Filter, we are interested in Linear Dynamic System(LDS), and Gaussian
noises.</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Transition probability: 
\(p\left(\mathbf{x}_{t} \mid \mathbf{x}_{t-1}\right) \sim \mathcal{N}\left(A
\mathbf{x}_{t-1}+B, Q_{t}\right)\)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Measurement probability:
\(p\left(y_{t} \mid \mathbf{x}_{t}\right) \sim \mathcal{N}\left(H \mathbf{x}_{t},
R_{t}\right)\)</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="3-model-paramters">3. Model Paramters</h4>

<h4 id="4-model-operations">4. Model Operations</h4>
<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Prediction:
\(p\left(x_{t} \mid \mathbf{y}_{1: t-1}\right)=\int_{x_{t-1}} p\left(x_{t} \mid
x_{t-1}\right) p\left(x_{t-1} \mid \mathbf{y}_{1: t-1}\right)\)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Update:
\(p\left(x_{t} \mid \mathbf{y}_{1: t}\right)=\frac{p\left(y_{t} \mid x_{t}\right)
p\left(x_{t} \mid \mathbf{y}_{1: t-1}\right)}{\int_{s_{t}} p\left(y_{t} \mid
s_{t}\right) p\left(d s_{t} \mid \mathbf{y}_{1: t-1}\right)}\)</p>
  </li>
</ol>

